                <head>346. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>Between January 30 and February 8, Saudi Arabian King <persName
                        corresp="#p_EMJSD1">Saud</persName> and other Saudi dignitaries visited
                    Washington and held extensive discussions with President <persName
                        corresp="#p_EMJSD1">Eisenhower</persName>, Secretary <persName
                        corresp="#p_DJF1">Dulles</persName>, and other high-ranking United States
                    officials. For documentation on the <persName corresp="#p_EMJSD1"
                        >Saud</persName> visit, including memoranda of discussions concerning the
                    Syrian situation, see <ref target="#d256">Documents 256</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
